":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over.mono_homMk\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">Over</span>.<span class=\"name\">mono_homMk</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₁}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₁, u₁}</a> <span class=\"fn\">T</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">X</span> : <span class=\"fn\">T</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">U </span><span class=\"fn\">V</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over\">Over</a> <span class=\"fn\">X</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">U</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Comma.left\">left</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">V</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Comma.left\">left</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Mono\">Mono</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">w</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">V</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Comma.hom\">hom</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">U</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Comma.hom\">hom</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Mono\">Mono</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over.homMk\">homMk</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">w</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over.mono_homMk","kind":"instance","line":323,"name":"CategoryTheory.Over.mono_homMk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.lean#L323-L324"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over.mono_of_mono_left\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">Over</span>.<span class=\"name\">mono_of_mono_left</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₁}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₁, u₁}</a> <span class=\"fn\">T</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">X</span> : <span class=\"fn\">T</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">f </span><span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over\">Over</a> <span class=\"fn\">X</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">g</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">hk</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Mono\">Mono</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">k</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CommaMorphism.left\">left</a></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Mono\">Mono</a> <span class=\"fn\">k</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `k.left` is a monomorphism, then `k` is a monomorphism. In other words, `Over.forget X` reflects\nmonomorphisms.\nThe converse of `CategoryTheory.Over.mono_left_of_mono`.\n\nThis lemma is not an instance, to avoid loops in type class inference.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Over.mono_of_mono_left","kind":"theorem","line":313,"name":"CategoryTheory.Over.mono_of_mono_left","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/Over/Basic.lean#L313-L321"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\